 only runtime dependency for meaningful coverage is Javassist, which is already a normal transitive dependency of ognl:ognl:3.3.5.\",\n  \"deterministic_setup\": [],\n  \"agent_guidance\": \"\",\n  \"risks\": [\n    \"OGNL exposes optional system properties such as ognl.security.manager, ognl.UseJDK9PlusAccessHandler, ognl.UseStricterInvocation, and ognl.UseFirstMatchGetSetLookup, but documentation/source indicate these are feature toggles or compatibility switches, not required setup for normal expression evaluation coverage.\",\n    \"The observed Java-run failure appears to be stale test behavior against 3.3.5 rather than missing dependency, Docker, environment variable, or required system property setup.\",\n    \"Tests that intentionally cover OGNL's optional SecurityManager path may be fragile on JDK 25 because SecurityManager APIs are deprecated/being removed; this is a test-design risk, not deterministic setup.\"\n  ]\n}", "textSignature": "{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_0a138952931617a8016a417cd3ce588190bacd2ed33c8eb704\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}], "api": "openai-responses", "provider": "OCA", "model": "oca/gpt-5.5", "usage": {"input": 822, "output": 1263, "cacheRead": 45568, "cacheWrite": 0, "totalTokens": 47653, "cost": {"input": 0, "output": 0, "cacheRead": 0, "cacheWrite": 0, "total": 0}}, "stopReason": "stop", "timestamp": 1782676671391, "responseId": "resp_0a138952931617a8016a417cc017008190a63197cac1f02431"}, "toolResults": []}
